  "text": [
    "In a lightning bolt",
    "of memory,",
    "I see our statue of Buddha",
    "(a wedding gift from Uncle Gene)",
    "which always sat",
    "on top of the speaker cabinet.",
    "When a visitor asked,",
    "\u201cSo, does Buddha like jazz?\u201d",
    "you said, \u201cI hope so.",
    "He\u2019s been getting it up the ass",
    "for a long time.\u201d"
  ],
  "title": "Love Poem",
  "year": ""
